  "2026-07-10T05:53:25.174Z",codex-root-20260709,"Verification evidence 2026-07-10: full sandbox suite passed 270 files / 5,505 tests with exact 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines. pm test-all over the seven active items passed 8 linked commands with 0 failures and 1 duplicate-safe skip. pnpm typecheck, contracts:check, lint (ESLint + 0 jscpd clones + static quality/token budget), docs-skills, context-eval, security scan, and audit all passed. Live CodeFactor reports A+ and 0 issues. Fresh packed npm install at /tmp/pm-cli-sdk-path-proof-XIsSsh activated 11 bundled packages in a path-target tracker, left caller extension files at zero, and passed CLI/SDK context plus isolated doctor with zero blocking failures. pm health is clean and history drift is zero."
  "2026-07-10T07:08:14.821Z",codex-root-20260709,"PR #491 review follow-up: verified Gemini findings against live runtime contracts. FailedExtensionLoad.error and FailedExtensionActivation.error are required strings, and loader formatUnknownError normalizes every unknown thrown value before constructing either record; optional chaining or re-stringification at the consumer would duplicate an already enforced invariant. The valid multi-target diagnostic-loss finding was fixed in the registration aggregator. Full coverage remains exact 100/100/100/100 and linked tests pass."
  "2026-07-10T08:05:01.776Z",codex-root-20260709,"Fresh PR #491 P1 closeout: --no-extensions is now an explicit failed verification state (ok=false, activated=false, degraded health, one blocking failure) without breaking legitimate lazy/metadata-only package activation. Runtime probes serialize the required PM_CLI_PACKAGE_ROOT override through the shared FIFO queue and restore it in finally. Packed install proof at /tmp/pm-pr491-packed-OkUpBn returned exit 1/degraded with extensions disabled and ok/activated on retry. Exact 100/100/100/100 coverage, strict quality, and linked tests pass."
